Class UpgradeHistoryEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.orm.entities.UpgradeHistoryEntity

  • @Entity
public class UpgradeHistoryEntity
extends Object
    The UpgradeHistoryEntity represents the version history of components participating in an upgrade or a downgrade.
